#!/bin/sh
# Build resume PDF from LaTeX source before pushing
echo "Building resume PDF..."
/Library/TeX/texbin/pdflatex -interaction=nonstopmode resume.tex > /dev/null 2>&1
if [ $? -ne 0 ]; then
    echo "ERROR: resume.tex failed to compile"
    exit 1
fi
cp resume.pdf static/cv/AnthonyDAndreaResume.pdf
git add static/cv/AnthonyDAndreaResume.pdf
git commit --amend --no-edit
echo "Resume PDF built and committed."
